      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 29 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 29 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>坎，習坎，有孚維心，亨。行有尚。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Kan, here repeated, shows the possession of sincerity, through which the mind is. penetrating. Action (in accordance with this) will be of high value.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
