      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 29 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 29 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：習坎，入于坎窞，凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows its subject in the double defile, and (yet) entering a cavern within it. There will be evil.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
