      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 29 六三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 29 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三：來之坎坎，險且枕，入于坎窞，勿用。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows its subject, whether he comes or goes ( =descends or ascends), confronted by a defile. All is peril to him and unrest. (His endeavours) will lead him into the cavern of the pit. There should be no action (in such a case).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
