      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 29 六四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 29 六四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六四：樽酒簋貳，用缶，納約自牖，終无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth SIX, divided, shows its subject (at a feast), with (simply) a bottle of spirits, and a subsidiary basket of rice, while (the cups and bowls) are (only) of earthenware. He introduces his important lessons (as his ruler's) intelligence admits. There will in the end be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
