      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 29 九五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 29 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五：坎不盈，只既平，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows the water of the defile not yet full, (so that it might flow away); but order will (soon) be brought about. There will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
